    dc:description "Fig. 45. Distribution of Begonia sect. Ephemera Moonlight in Peru and surrounding countries. A. B. fischeri Schrank (red). B. B. hirtella Link (red). Black lines indicate country borders, grey lines indicate major administrative divisions, blue lines indicate rivers, and shading indicates elevation." ;
